56:57.193 --> 56:59.684
No! I don't
need this!

56:59.763 --> 57:01.162
Hey, you fuck!

57:01.231 --> 57:04.132
Hey, goddamn you!

57:04.200 --> 57:05.690
Goddamn it.

57:05.802 --> 57:07.703
I am a fucking Vietnam veteran!

57:09.940 --> 57:10.838
This isn't...

