57:40.306 --> 57:41.672
Ron. It's Ron Kovic.

57:41.742 --> 57:43.573
Sorry, man. Ron.

57:43.644 --> 57:45.942
You... You are a doctor?

57:46.013 --> 57:48.106
It's the Vietnam war.
Cutbacks.

57:48.182 --> 57:50.377
