01:05:19.972 --> 01:05:22.406
and their face changes,
the eyes...

01:05:22.474 --> 01:05:25.443
the voice, the way
they look at you.

01:05:25.511 --> 01:05:27.411
I know, but people here,

01:05:27.479 --> 01:05:29.913
they don't give a shit
about the war.

01:05:29.982 --> 01:05:32.884
