01:05:54.475 --> 01:05:56.205
For what?

01:05:56.278 --> 01:05:57.404
For lies?

01:05:57.479 --> 01:05:59.572
For bullshit lies?

01:06:06.321 --> 01:06:07.789
They burn the flag.

01:06:07.857 --> 01:06:09.256
