01:06:38.690 --> 01:06:40.157
How can we win?

01:06:40.225 --> 01:06:41.658
Tommy, what's the matter?

01:06:41.727 --> 01:06:42.625
Nothing.

01:06:42.695 --> 01:06:44.128
